"{\"uid\": \"tmz.com-2024-08-06-imane-khelif-wins-semi-final-fight-olympic-gold\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Algerian boxerImane Khelifwill fight for a gold medal on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 64, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversial pugilist emerged from her semi-final bout with Thai boxerJanjaem Suwannaphengby unanimous decision in Paris on Tuesday ... making her one of two fighters left standing.\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 186, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999868407746357, \"rank\": 1.3159398585482884e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was welcomed by a mostly supportive crowd ... with some even waving Algeria's green and white flag, and chanting \\\"Imane!\\\"\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9996131362537541, \"rank\": 0.0003798511673774865, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, Imane's arguably the most polarizing athlete at the entire Olympic Games ... this after questions wereraised about her gender, and whether or not Khelif should be eligible to compete.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC, as well as other officials, have stood firmly by Khelif ... making it clear the fighter has met any/all requirements.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999969305, \"rank\": 3.027084872647348e-12, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Imane, she's admittedly been affected by the controversy ... but she's got an idea of how to respond.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Win.\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"God willing, this crisis will culminate in a gold medal, and that would be the best response,\\\" the fighter said in an interview conducted in Arabic before being translated into English.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane's opponent is not yet known ... that'll be determined on Wednesday in the other semifinal matchup.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What is known -- Khelif's one win away from the gold.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay tuned ...\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes!\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send me email updates and offers from TMZ and its Affiliates.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"score\": 0.9995591380065372, \"rank\": 0.00044105643851281, \"text\": \"TMZ\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By subscribing, I agree to thePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Use\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": []}]}"